name: (Rare) DuCat / DNA Cerulian
bio: Hey cutie! I'm (Rare) DuCat / DNA Cerulian. All you need to know about me is I hate wet food with a passion. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their snap-backs and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. We can be friends, but keep the ultra purrsonal stuff to yourself, please.
